latestPosts.caption: Girls run to @thepatchee.lk cuz this bag is EVERYTHING!! This is that one bag you must have simply because it looks so good and blends with everything! it has gone to meetings with me, various kinds of events, brunch, dinners, shoots you name it! It’s so functional- I can fit my wallet, face powder, about 7-8 lip products, hand cream, phone, snacks and much more 😂 not even joking it holds soo much! And best part is- it has a hard exterior so even if you’re clumsy like me, no worries 😉

@bayleee.srilanka is now at @havelockcitymall 💗‼️🤩🥳

Fell in love with almost all the pieces from their new collection- and I’m sure you guys are gonna love it too so definitely check it out

Silhouette that compliments you 🥰 first time at @kinstudio_cmb (where they have both @loislondoninc and @kingandlois ) and all i wondered was why I haven’t come here before!!!!!! because I instantly fell in love with some of the pieces I saw right away, specially the orange dress I’m wearing. 

They had a big collection with some casuals, glamour wear and even cotton shirts for men. Loved their studio style set up where you get a wholistic experience just walking in their doors

Located at 3 Ascot Avenue (easily spotted as Kin Studio on Gmaps) and they are open till 5.30pm if you guys want to have a look. 

They also have few sale items on display up to 70% off 🥰
